    JBookmarkItem, JFacetAddItem, JFacetOpenItem, JFileOpenItem, JWeblinkItem

    public class JItemPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    This class represents the general-purpose graphical item in the list console. It contains a title, an icon and a locator , which will be executed by the click on the item.

    imasa
